description:
Taken from the historic, inaugural AmericaFest event, Human Events Daily Host Jack Posobiec speaks directly to the youth of our nation in a rousing call to action to preserve and protect the foundation of the United States: patriotism, family and God.

Here is your daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
